✅ Steps to Create User in Jenkins (UI Method)
Login to Jenkins as admin.

Click on "Manage Jenkins" from the left menu.

Go to "Manage Users".

Click "Create User".

Fill in:

Username

Password

Full Name

Email

Click Create User.

✅ Bonus (If "Manage Users" not visible)
You may need to install the "Matrix Authorization Strategy" plugin and enable user security:

Go to Manage Jenkins → Configure Global Security.

Enable "Jenkins own user database".

Enable "Allow users to sign up" (optional).

Save and restart Jenkins.
